headline_main: Transgender Lives: Your Stories: Laura A. Jacobs

abstract: Passing means if people don't know me, they see me as female.  I am slowly starting to believe it myself -- it takes awhile to shake one's old identity after so long.

headline_main: Transgender Lives: Your Stories: Seamus Johnston

abstract: I know that a lot of times it seems like it would be easier just to give up. And I know that it's selfish of me to ask this of you, but please stay here.
